link:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 22, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104jpi1665702811897.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jpi1665702811897.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jpi1665702811897.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"jpi1665702811897\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                                      \n Triggers\n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The Triggers pane lists the triggers available for the menu item selected in the Structure pane. Use the Triggers pane to select the trigger you want to edit.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jpi1665702811897__section_w115ab1b5b1_w116ab1b5_w117ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\"></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jpi1665702811897__section_dx4_jhg_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d256493e56\">Icons</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"jpi1665702811897__ul_m5h_khg_5cc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jpi1665702811897__li_d3497e1_d3498e1_d3499e1\">\n<img alt=\"Graphical content\" class=\"image\" id=\"jpi1665702811897__image_o5h_khg_5cc\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/u7_trgstd.gif?_LANG=enus\"/> Trigger contains code and does not inherit. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jpi1665702811897__li_d3500e1_d3501e1_d3502e1\">\n<img alt=\"Graphical content\" class=\"image\" id=\"jpi1665702811897__image_q5h_khg_5cc\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/u7_trgemp.gif?_LANG=enus\"/> Trigger is empty. </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jpi1665702811897__section_cm4_khg_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d256493e83\">Actions</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jpi1665702811897__p_d7061e1_d7062e1_d7063e1\">You can navigate and sort triggers, and manage tags using\n        menu items are available from the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Edit</span> menu, pop-up menu, and tool\n        bar.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"jpi1665702811897__table_d602e1_d603e1_d604e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Trigger List Menu Items</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"jpi1665702811897__table_d602e1_d603e1_d604e1__entry__1\">Action/Menu Item </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"jpi1665702811897__table_d602e1_d603e1_d604e1__entry__2\">Tool Bar Icon </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"jpi1665702811897__table_d602e1_d603e1_d604e1__entry__3\">Description </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jpi1665702811897__table_d602e1_d603e1_d604e1__entry__1\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Sort Triggers</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jpi1665702811897__table_d602e1_d603e1_d604e1__entry__2\"></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jpi1665702811897__table_d602e1_d603e1_d604e1__entry__3\">Sort triggers by name or by type (based on the trigger\n                icons). Click the header of the Trigger List to reverse the sort order. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jpi1665702811897__table_d602e1_d603e1_d604e1__entry__1\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Add Manual Tag</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jpi1665702811897__table_d602e1_d603e1_d604e1__entry__2\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"jpi1665702811897__fig_mmp_lhg_5cc\">\n<img alt=\"Graphical content\" class=\"image\" id=\"jpi1665702811897__image_nmp_lhg_5cc\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/addmanualtag.gif?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jpi1665702811897__table_d602e1_d603e1_d604e1__entry__3\">Mark a trigger for later reference. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jpi1665702811897__table_d602e1_d603e1_d604e1__entry__1\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Clear Manual Tags</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jpi1665702811897__table_d602e1_d603e1_d604e1__entry__2\"></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jpi1665702811897__table_d602e1_d603e1_d604e1__entry__3\">Clear all manually defined tags. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jpi1665702811897__table_d602e1_d603e1_d604e1__entry__1\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Delete Manual Tag</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jpi1665702811897__table_d602e1_d603e1_d604e1__entry__2\"></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jpi1665702811897__table_d602e1_d603e1_d604e1__entry__3\">Delete the selected manual tag. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jpi1665702811897__table_d602e1_d603e1_d604e1__entry__1\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Check Syntax</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jpi1665702811897__table_d602e1_d603e1_d604e1__entry__2\">\n<div class=\"p\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"jpi1665702811897__fig_qmp_lhg_5cc\">\n<img alt=\"Graphical content\" class=\"image\" id=\"jpi1665702811897__image_rmp_lhg_5cc\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/checksyntaxmodified.gif?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</div>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jpi1665702811897__table_d602e1_d603e1_d604e1__entry__3\">Check the ProcScript syntax in all modified triggers.\n                Triggers that contain errors are tagged and placed in the Tag Tree. Double-click the\n                tagged trigger to edit it. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_4811162\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_4811162\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Triggers Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 22, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Triggers The Triggers pane lists the triggers available for the menu item selected in the Structure pane. Use the Triggers pane to select the trigger you want to edit. Icons Trigger contains code and does not inherit. Trigger is empty. Actions You can navigate and sort triggers, and manage tags using menu items are available from the Edit menu, pop-up menu, and tool bar. Table 1. Trigger List Menu Items Action/Menu Item Tool Bar Icon Description Sort Triggers Sort triggers by name or by type (based on the trigger icons). Click the header of the Trigger List to reverse the sort order. Add Manual Tag Mark a trigger for later reference. Clear Manual Tags Clear all manually defined tags. Delete Manual Tag Delete the selected manual tag. Check Syntax Check the ProcScript syntax in all modified triggers. Triggers that contain errors are tagged and placed in the Tag Tree. Double-click the tagged trigger to edit it. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}